# Start the app at container startup. `bell-schedule` and `bhs-calendars` are
# PyPI deps now (see pyproject.toml -- no `[tool.uv.sources]`), so `uv run`
# resolves them from the registry; no `../bells` symlink is needed. To develop
# the library alongside the app, add a path/editable source under
# `[tool.uv.sources]` -- not here.
./serve.sh -d
